note right of ExpenseCreateComponent
  FR-02.1 UI entry point.
  Builds the reactive form,
  loads categories and currencies,
  previews conversion,
  dispatches create actions,
  and delegates persistence to ExpenseService.
end note

note right of ExpenseService
  Enforces business rules for:
  - mandatory date/amount/currency/category
  - positive amount
  - supported currency
  - active category
  - active signed-in user
  Persists Expense as Draft.
end note

note right of CurrencyService
  Supports the implemented
  multi-currency enhancement,
  but FR-02.1 still fundamentally
  requires currency as a mandatory field.
end note

